b'$SI The go-to bank for the cryptocurrency industry. Real-time USD settlement between counterparties, used by some of the largest exchanges in the world.\nThe Silvergate Exchange Network (SEN) enables digital currency and institutional investor clients to send U.S. dollars 24/7/365'

b'$SI serves as the middleman between digital currency exchanges like Coinbase and institutional investors looking to trade crypto assets. \n$SI is a real-time payments network, meaning it can clear transfers instantly around the clock, 365 days a year.'
